            "is_accepted": false,
            "last_activity_date": 1359764981,
            "creation_date": 1359764981,
            "body": "<p>If your constraint is to traverse the array from the start, Store the index as and when you see <code>0<\/code> into a variable and as you complete the loop just print the variable<\/p>\n\n<pre><code>int lastindex;\nfor(int i=0;i&lt;x.length;i++){\n         if(x[i]==0){\n             lastindex=i;\n}\nSystem.out.println(lastindex); \n<\/code><\/pre>\n",
            "answer_id": 14657298,
            "question_id": 14657278
        },
        {
            "owner": {
                "profile_image": "https://www.gravatar.com/avatar/4b3f8f3525c4e7c41285dff7a3204098?s=256&d=identicon&r=PG",
