            "last_activity_date": 1359770354,
            "creation_date": 1359770354,
            "body": "<pre><code>public static int lastZero(int[] x){\n        int temp=0;\n        for(int i=0;i&lt;x.length;i++){\n         if(x[i]==0){\n             temp=i;\n         }\n        }\n        System.out.println(temp);\n        return 0;\n    }\n<\/code><\/pre>\n\n<p>This would give the desired output.<\/p>\n",
            "answer_id": 14657840,
